<h1 class="principal-title">A global movement for cruelty free cosmetics</h1>
<h2 class="sub-heading">Sign our petition to stop animal testing in the cosmetic industry</h2> </br>

<section id="main-img">
  <br>
<p>As hard as it is to believe, animal experiments for cosmetics continue even though non-animal tests are widely available</p>
<p>Take action: The best way to stop companies from using animals is to refuse to purchase their products and to sign our petition to show our disagreement!</p>
<br><br>
  <img src="no_animal_testing.jpg" alt="no_animal_testing">
</section>

<section id="user-input" class="card">
<h2>Please join our petition today</h2>
{{errorMessage}}
<form method="POST" action="/register">
  <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{csrfToken}}">
  <div class="text-input">
    <label for="firstname">First name:</label><br>
    <input type="text" name="firstname" id="firstname" placeholder="Firstname" pattern="[A-Za-z]+" title ="Please enter a valid first name" required><br>
    <label for="lastname">Last name:</label><br>
    <input type="text" name="lastname" id="lastname" placeholder="Lastname"  pattern="[A-Za-z]+" title ="Please enter a valid first name" required><br>
    <label for="email">Email:</label><br>
    <input type="email" name="email" id="email" placeholder="email" required><br>
    <label for="password">Password:</label><br>
    <input type="password" name="password" id="pasword" placeholder="password" required><br>
  </div>
  <input type="submit" value="Sign Up" id="input-submit">
</form>

<h4>If already a member, please <a href="/login">log in</a>.</h4>
</section>
